de.dfki.adom.rest.nodes

Class Header

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.restlet.Restlet
      • de.dfki.adom.rest.nodes.Component
        • de.dfki.adom.rest.nodes.Header
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.restlet.Uniform

    public class Header
extends Component

    A Component to handle the retrieval of the object memory's header via the REST interface.

    Represents the "header" node in the REST tree and handles HTTP requests going there.

    Author:
    Jens Haupert
